People are Buzzing About our Glowing Plant
We launched The Glowing Plant in 2013 as the first synthetic biology campaign ever on Kickstarter. People loved it. We raised $484,000—over 700x our original goal. It was the first step in getting bioengineering projects in the hands of everyday people. 





